	   <tr><td colspan=2>Hmmm well thats a hard question and one that will be argued...&nbsp;&nbsp;I have a dark elf.. I like the race and thats what a lot of people choose...  Erudites have the best starting int by far... Iksar make cool nec cuz they just look damn cool. :)  They have enhanced regeneration and i heard that at higher lvls  this is a bonus for necros when using the call of bones type spell for mana... These are the 3 i favor...  if i did it all over again i would prolly create an iksar..  Dont get me wrong i love my dark elf, but you dont see many iksar nec...  Lots of dark elfs... not as many erudites.. not many at all iksar....  well i dunno  i am sure you will get many more about this argument...  so read on.. :)<br>&nbsp;<br>Sphoenix Darkfever</td></tr>
