<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=99790196958633></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f99790196958633><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=classes.html?class=14&mid=99790196958633>RE: Help me out plz...</a> <a id=fs8 href=classes.html?class=14&mid=99790196958633#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <span id= >Anonymous</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Wed, Aug 15th 2:59 PM 2001</td>
