	   <tr><td colspan=2>Sphoenix is right...I also have a DE necro and if I had to do it all again I would take an Iksar due to regen.&nbsp;&nbsp;At higher levels, you need the regen to offset some of the hp burn you get with Lich...Lich eats about 31 hp every 6 seconds...with some regen, it minimizes the bleeding...and when you get the 60th level mana conversion spell...you burn about 46 hp per 6 seconds...that is going to be insane!<br><br>Go with the Iksar...70% of the time you are going to look like a skeleton anyway!<br><br>Ishtarra Gemeinseele, Talion Defiler of the Dirty Soul<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 >&nbsp;</td><td align=right valign=bottom>
